title: Thomas Rhett On His Dad’s Biggest Complaints About Him + Bobby’s Dog Is Chewing Again + Lunchbox The Parking Enforcer Busts Out The Boot
itunes:title: Thomas Rhett On His Dad’s Biggest Complaints About Him + Bobby’s Dog Is Chewing Again + Lunchbox The Parking Enforcer Busts Out The Boot
description:
We talk to Thomas Rhett about being one of CMT’s Artists of the Year, his sold out Madison Square Garden Show and his dad’s two biggest complaints about him. Bobby’s dog has unfortunately started chewing again and Lunchbox caught someone parking in Bobby’s spot at work.
